---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../components/Disclaimer.astro';

// Yield Lab decisions — sourced research candidates run through the ADR-YL-008 mandate
// (spread over the live RWA floor ~3.4%, every bp risk-explained). RESEARCH, not offerings.
// Source of truth: docs/decision_index.md + docs/underwriting_rubric.md (public repo).
// Verdict tone: ok=ADVANCE/paper, warn=WATCH/conditional, danger=REFUSE, muted=NO-EDGE.
const decisions = [
  { id: 'PT-sUSDe', mech: 'Pendle fixed carry', mechRu: 'Pendle фикс-carry',
    yield: '~11.2%', spread: '~780 bps', tone: 'ok', verdict: 'ADVANCE → paper', verdictRu: 'ADVANCE → пейпер',
    why: 'Fixed-to-maturity removes the funding-flip tail; USDe solvency stress-validated (Oct-2025 crash: overcollateralized throughout). Capacity ~single-digit $M/maturity.',
    whyRu: 'Фиксация до погашения убирает funding-хвост; платёжеспособность USDe прошла стресс окт-2025 (оставался overcollateralized). Ёмкость ~single-digit $M/срок.' },
  { id: 'PT-USDe', mech: 'Pendle fixed carry', mechRu: 'Pendle фикс-carry',
    yield: '~8.8%', spread: '~540 bps', tone: 'ok', verdict: 'ADVANCE (capped)', verdictRu: 'ADVANCE (с cap)',
    why: 'Same fundable structure, but same Ethena underlying as PT-sUSDe → shares one cap, not extra diversification (~70% of Pendle TVL is Ethena).',
    whyRu: 'Та же fundable-структура, но тот же Ethena-underlying, что и PT-sUSDe → общий cap, не доп. диверсификация (~70% TVL Pendle = Ethena).' },
  { id: 'Maple syrupUSDC', mech: 'Institutional credit', mechRu: 'Институц. кредит',
    yield: '~9–12%', spread: '~180 bps+', tone: 'warn', verdict: 'WATCH', verdictRu: 'WATCH',
    why: 'Bounded credit — loans overcollateralized 120–170% at qualified custody (Anchorage/BitGo/Copper), ~3yr zero-loss. DD-gated (v1 lost $50M in 2022).',
    whyRu: 'Ограниченный кредит — займы overcollateralized 120–170% в qualified-custody, ~3 года без потерь. Под DD (v1 потерял $50M в 2022).' },
  { id: 'Centrifuge DROP', mech: 'RWA senior tranche', mechRu: 'RWA senior-транш',
    yield: '~8%', spread: '~460 bps', tone: 'warn', verdict: 'WATCH', verdictRu: 'WATCH',
    why: 'Senior tranche bounded by a real junior (TIN) first-loss buffer + real RWA cash flows. Per-pool off-chain DD required (buffer depth, asset quality).',
    whyRu: 'Senior-транш ограничен реальным junior (TIN) first-loss буфером + реальные RWA-cashflow. Нужен per-pool off-chain DD (глубина буфера, качество активов).' },
  { id: 'Aave V3 USDC', mech: 'Blue-chip lending', mechRu: 'Blue-chip кредит',
    yield: '~3.45%', spread: '~5 bps', tone: 'muted', verdict: 'NO-EDGE', verdictRu: 'NO-EDGE',
    why: 'The safest, deepest DeFi lending pays ≈ the floor — no spread to underwrite. Hold the T-bill floor instead. Proof that spread must be earned by risk.',
    whyRu: 'Самый безопасный/глубокий DeFi-кредит платит ≈ floor — нет спреда для андеррайтинга. Держи T-bill floor. Доказательство: спред покупается риском.' },
  { id: 'Ethena sUSDe (spot)', mech: 'Funding carry', mechRu: 'Funding-carry',
    yield: '~3.9% (was 9–11%)', spread: '~46 bps', tone: 'danger', verdict: 'lean-REFUSE', verdictRu: 'lean-REFUSE',
    why: 'Floating funding carry is an unbounded tail (funding-flip, CEX-counterparty, ~1.1% reserve). Thin spread today does not pay for the tail.',
    whyRu: 'Плавающий funding-carry — неограниченный хвост (funding-flip, CEX-контрагент, резерв ~1.1%). Тонкий спред сегодня не окупает хвост.' },
  { id: 'Curve/Convex LP', mech: 'Stable LP + emissions', mechRu: 'Stable-LP + эмиссии',
    yield: '~4–10%', spread: 'mostly emissions', tone: 'danger', verdict: 'REFUSE', verdictRu: 'REFUSE',
    why: 'The attractive part is CRV/CVX token emissions — a subsidy, not risk-comp. Strip emissions → base fees ≈ floor-parity. Value what you keep if rewards → 0.',
    whyRu: 'Привлекательная часть — эмиссии CRV/CVX, субсидия, не risk-comp. Убери эмиссии → базовые комиссии ≈ floor. Оцени, что останется при rewards → 0.' },
  { id: 'Goldfinch Senior', mech: 'Uncollat. EM credit', mechRu: 'Uncollat EM-кредит',
    yield: '~10–14%', spread: '~660–1060 bps', tone: 'danger', verdict: 'REFUSE (dead)', verdictRu: 'REFUSE (мёртв)',
    why: 'The tail fired at scale — protocol formally winding down after ~$50M of defaults stranded depositors ~3 years. A "senior" label does not bound a thin first-loss buffer.',
    whyRu: 'Хвост сработал в масштабе — протокол сворачивается после ~$50M дефолтов, депозиторы застряли ~3 года. Ярлык «senior» не ограничивает тонкий first-loss буфер.' },
  { id: 'Resolv RLP', mech: 'First-loss tranche', mechRu: 'First-loss транш',
    yield: '~20–30%', spread: '~1700–2700 bps', tone: 'danger', verdict: 'REFUSE (hard)', verdictRu: 'REFUSE (жёстко)',
    why: 'The yield is payment to absorb first loss with self-balancing leverage — and the tail already fired: a 2026 mint exploit (~$25M extracted, USDe −39% depeg, TVL $400M→$9M).',
    whyRu: 'Доход — плата за поглощение first-loss с самобалансирующимся плечом — и хвост уже сработал: эксплойт минта 2026 (~$25M, депег −39%, TVL $400M→$9M).' },
];
const toneClass = {
  ok:     'text-ok border-ok-border bg-ok-bg',
  warn:   'text-warn border-warn-border bg-warn-bg',
  danger: 'text-danger border-danger-border bg-danger-bg',
  muted:  'text-white/40 border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03]',
};
---

<Layout
  title="Yield Lab — Research Decisions | earn-defi.com"
  description="The Yield Lab evaluates live stablecoin yields against the RWA floor: every basis point of spread must be explained by a measurable, accepted risk, or it is refused. Research decisions with verdicts and evidence levels — not investment offerings."
  canonical="https://earn-defi.com/yield-lab"
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="pt-20 pb-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent-500/10 border border-accent-700/40 text-xs text-accent-300 font-medium">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent-400" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span data-ru="Решения, а не предложения">Decisions, not offerings</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight" data-ru="Йилд-лаб">
        Yield Lab
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl" data-ru="Мы оцениваем живую доходность стейблкоинов против RWA-floor (~3.4%). Каждый базисный пункт спреда должен объясняться измеримым, принятым риском — иначе отказ. Публикуем и отказы: это и есть продукт.">
        We judge live stablecoin yield against the RWA floor (~3.4%). Every basis point of spread must
        be explained by a measurable, accepted risk — or it is refused. We publish the refusals too:
        that discipline is the product.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Honesty banner — non-negotiable framing -->
    <section class="pb-2">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-warn-border bg-warn-bg p-5">
        <p class="text-xs text-warn uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-2" data-ru="Как это читать">How to read this</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed" data-ru="Это research-суждения (уровень доказательности L2 — из публичных источников на 2026-07-02), а НЕ live-доходности, не оффер и не инвест-совет. «ADVANCE → пейпер» означает бумажный advisory-тест без капитала, отдельно от нашего go-live трека. Цифры дрейфуют; источник истины — docs/decision_index.md и docs/underwriting_rubric.md в публичном репозитории.">
          These are research judgements (evidence level L2 — from public sources as of 2026-07-02), <strong class="text-white/85">not</strong>
          live returns, an offer, or investment advice. "ADVANCE → paper" means an advisory paper test with
          <strong class="text-white/85">no capital</strong>, separate from our go-live track. Numbers drift; the source of truth is
          <code class="text-accent-300">docs/decision_index.md</code> + <code class="text-accent-300">docs/underwriting_rubric.md</code> in the public repo.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mt-3" data-ru="Fundable-кандидаты (ADVANCE/WATCH) теперь пишут advisory бумажный трек в Strategy Lab (агент com.spa.strategy_lab_paper, ежечасно) — без капитала, ОТДЕЛЬНО от go-live трека. Форвардные кривые набираются со временем; это симуляция при sourced-ставке, не реализованная доходность.">
          The fundable candidates (ADVANCE/WATCH) now record an <strong class="text-white/85">advisory</strong> paper track in the
          Strategy Lab (agent <code class="text-accent-300">com.spa.strategy_lab_paper</code>, hourly) — <strong class="text-white/85">no capital</strong>,
          separate from the go-live track. Forward curves accrue over time; this is a simulation at the sourced rate, not realized yield.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The decisions table -->
    <section class="py-10 border-t border-white/5">
      <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-6" data-ru="Решения на живых данных">Decisions on live data</p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        {decisions.map((d) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] p-5 hover:border-white/15 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-2 flex-wrap">
              <div class="min-w-0">
                <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white font-mono">{d.id}</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40" data-ru={d.mechRu}>{d.mech}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-sm text-white/70 font-mono tabular-nums">{d.yield}</span>
                <span class={`inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full border text-xs font-medium ${toneClass[d.tone]}`} data-ru={d.verdictRu}>{d.verdict}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 text-xs text-white/35 font-mono">
              <span data-ru="спред над floor">spread over floor</span>
              <span class="text-white/60 tabular-nums">{d.spread}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed" data-ru={d.whyRu}>{d.why}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The non-Ethena ladder -->
    <section class="py-10 border-t border-white/5">
      <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-3" data-ru="Не-Ethena лестница">The non-Ethena ladder</p>
      <p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-6" data-ru="Настоящие 8-12% на стейблах структурно доминируются Ethena (funding-carry). Диверсификация — по КЛАССУ АКТИВА, не по цепи (уход на Base просто возвращает к Ethena). Вот честная лестница без Ethena-концентрации:">
        The real 8-12% in stablecoins is structurally dominated by Ethena (funding-carry). You diversify
        by <strong class="text-white/85">asset class</strong>, not by chain (hopping to Base just re-routes to Ethena). Here is the
        honest ladder without Ethena concentration:
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-3">
          <div class="min-w-0"><span class="text-sm text-white font-medium" data-ru="RWA floor (T-bill)">RWA floor (T-bill)</span><span class="text-xs text-white/40 ml-2" data-ru="глубина ~$15B">~$15B deep</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-sm text-white/70 font-mono tabular-nums">~3.4%</span><span class="text-xs text-white/40 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-white/10">BASELINE</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-3">
          <div class="min-w-0"><span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Steakhouse overcollat</span><span class="text-xs text-white/40 ml-2" data-ru="immutable Morpho Blue, глубина ~$6.6B">immutable Morpho Blue, ~$6.6B</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-sm text-white/70 font-mono tabular-nums">~4.5–6.5%</span><span class="text-xs text-ok px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-ok-border bg-ok-bg">ADVANCE · Core</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-3">
          <div class="min-w-0"><span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Maple syrupUSDC</span><span class="text-xs text-white/40 ml-2" data-ru="кредит, 160%+ overcollat, 0 дефолтов >$600M">credit, 160%+ collat, 0 defaults >$600M</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-sm text-white/70 font-mono tabular-nums">~4.7%</span><span class="text-xs text-ok px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-ok-border bg-ok-bg" data-ru="ADVANCE · Core (cap)">ADVANCE · Core</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-3">
          <div class="min-w-0"><span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Centrifuge DROP</span><span class="text-xs text-white/40 ml-2" data-ru="RWA senior-транш, junior first-loss">RWA senior, junior first-loss</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-sm text-white/70 font-mono tabular-nums">~8%</span><span class="text-xs text-warn px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-warn-border bg-warn-bg">WATCH</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-lg border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-3 opacity-60">
          <div class="min-w-0"><span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Notional fCash</span><span class="text-xs text-white/40 ml-2" data-ru="правильный класс, TVL схлопнулся ~$3M">right class, TVL collapsed ~$3M</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-shrink-0"><span class="text-xs text-danger px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-danger-border bg-danger-bg" data-ru="ёмкость мертва">capacity-dead</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-3" data-ru="Правило «выбери два»">The pick-two rule</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed" data-ru="Нельзя одновременно {8-12% · диверсифицировано · не-Ethena · в масштабе}. Диверсифицированная не-Ethena книга (40% floor / 30% overcollat / 20% Maple / 10% Centrifuge) даёт ≈4.75% — bounded, ~135 bps над floor, но НЕ 8-12%. Чтобы получить 8-12% без Ethena — нужна концентрация в higher-risk кредите. Уход от Ethena — правильное риск-решение, и он стоит доходности. Этот озвученный trade-off и есть продукт.">
          You can't have all four at once — 8-12%, diversified, non-Ethena, and at scale. A diversified non-Ethena book
          (40% floor / 30% overcollat / 20% Maple / 10% Centrifuge) blends to <strong class="text-white/85">≈4.75%</strong> — bounded,
          ~135 bps over the floor, but <strong class="text-white/85">not</strong> 8-12%. To reach 8-12% without Ethena you must
          concentrate in higher-risk credit. Diversifying away from Ethena is the right risk decision, and it
          costs yield. That stated trade-off is the product. Full analysis: <code class="text-accent-300">docs/non_ethena_ladder.md</code>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The one principle -->
    <section class="py-10 border-t border-white/5">
      <p class="text-xs text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4" data-ru="Один принцип">The one principle</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/75 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl" data-ru="Доходность ⟂ фандабилити. Самый большой заголовочный процент (Resolv 20–30%) получил самый жёсткий отказ — хвост уже сработал. Самый маленький объяснённый спред (~160–780 bps) — единственные fundable. Спред покупается принятым риском, никогда не бесплатен.">
        Yield is inverse to fundability. The biggest headline number (Resolv 20–30%) drew the hardest
        refusal — its tail already fired. The smallest <em>explained</em> spreads (~160–780 bps) are the
        only fundable ones. Spread is bought with accepted risk; it is never free.
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Disclaimer />
</Layout>
